ergence will be achieved by taking $\\gamma_{\\text{opt}}=2/\\alpha$.\nNumerical examples are provided to demonstrate our theoretical analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Jan 2022 17:19:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-25"}
