 close-in ($<$\n0.1 au) binary dipper is rarely reported so far, further investigation will\nreveal the new aspect of the disk evolution and planetary formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 05:12:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
