 indicates that the change of the physical properties of the\nrecurring CIR from one rotation to another is not qualitatively different from\nthe change of the physical properties of CIRs originating from different CHs.\nFinally, the obtained generic CIR example, analyzed on the basis of superposed\nepoch analysis, can be used as a reference for testing future models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 12:04:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
