 real solar\nobservations, whenever the 3D fieldline shape is known. The enhancement in\nenergy flux associated with magneto-acoustic waves near nulls may have\nimportant implications in the formation of jets and impulsive plasma flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 14:17:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
